<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1174.105851.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Superturmaspis schizosoma (Takagi, 1970), revived combination, adult female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/892451" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1174.105851.figure6>
    dc:description "Figure 6. The ML tree based on the concatenated data of 28 S and EF- 1 α. Bootstrap values (BV) are shown on each node. Orange shading represents the position of Superturmaspis schizosoma (Takagi, 1970) on the phylogenetic tree." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/892452" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1174.105851.figure7>
    dc:description "Figure 7. The BI tree based on the concatenated data of 28 S and EF- 1 α. Posterior probabilities (pp) are shown on each node. Orange shading represents the position of Superturmaspis schizosoma (Takagi, 1970) on the phylogenetic tree." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/892453" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

